headline: A Look At ONEOK (OKE) Valuation After Dividend Increase And New Independent Directors
summary: ONEOK (OKE) is back in focus after the board approved a higher quarterly dividend and added two independent directors, moves that put income policy and boardroom oversight at center stage for investors. See our latest analysis for ONEOK. Despite the higher dividend and fresh board appointments, ONEOK’s recent share price has been choppy, with a 1-day share price return decline of 4.89% and a 7-day share price return decline of 2.81%.
